UserOptionDefinition.CRD_SlurpPlant_C.MaximumRegrowths.Descri: Determines how many times the plant can regrow after launching a projectile or being destroyed. This applies across the device's entire lifetime and is unaffected by Enable and Disable.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_WildsPlants_Parent_C.MaximumRegro: Determines how many times the plant can regrow after launching a projectile or being destroyed. This applies across the device's entire lifetime and is unaffected by Enable and Disable.
UserOptionDefinition.CRD_SlurpPlant_C.InitialDelay.Descriptio: Determines the delay before the plant grows for the first time. This timer resets if the device is disabled. If you're too close, the plant won't grow until you move away.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_WildsPlants_Parent_C.InitialDelay: Determines the delay before the plant grows for the first time. This timer resets if the device is disabled. If you're too close, the plant won't grow until you move away.
UserOptionDefinition.CRD_SlurpPlant_C.RegrowthDelay.Descripti: Determines the delay before the plant regrows after launching a projectile or being destroyed. This timer resets if the device is disabled. If you're too close, the plant won't grow until you move away.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_WildsPlants_Parent_C.RegrowthDela: Determines the delay before the plant regrows after launching a projectile or being destroyed. This timer resets if the device is disabled. If you're too close, the plant won't grow until you move away.
UserOptionDefinition.CRD_SlurpPlant_C.EnabledDuringPhase.Desc: Determines the game phases during which the device will be enabled. During Create, launching or exploding the plant will not cause damage.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_WildsPlants_Parent_C.EnabledDurin: Determines the game phases during which the device will be enabled. During Create, launching or exploding the plant will not cause damage.
UserOptionDefinition.CRD_SlurpPlant_C.LaunchOnHit.Description: Determines whether hitting the plant will launch a projectile that explodes on impact. If set to OFF, hitting the plant will cause it to explode immediately.
Determines whether hitting the plant will launch a projectile that explodes on impact. If set to OFF, hitting the plant will cause it to explode immediately.
UserOptionDefinition.CRD_SlurpPlant_C.InfiniteRegrowths.Descr: Determines whether the plant can always regrow after launching a projectile or being destroyed.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_WildsPlants_Parent_C.InfiniteRegr: Determines whether the plant can always regrow after launching a projectile or being destroyed.
UserOptionDefinition.CRD_SlurpPlant_C.GrowAutomatically.Descr: Determines whether the plant can automatically grow, or if it can only grow when the device receives a signal. This does not apply while editing the island. INITIAL ONLY - The plant can grow once automatically. REGROWTH ONLY - The plant can grow automatically after launching a projectile or being destroyed.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_WildsPlants_Parent_C.GrowAutomati: Determines whether the plant can automatically grow, or if it can only grow when the device receives a signal. This does not apply while editing the island. INITIAL ONLY - The plant can grow once automatically. REGROWTH ONLY - The plant can grow automatically after launching a projectile or being destroyed.
UserOptionDefinition.CRD_SlurpPlant_C.HideWhenDisabled.Descri: Determines whether the plant is hidden while this device is disabled. SHOW LEAVES - Only the leaves will be visible while this device is disabled.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_WildsPlants_Parent_C.HideWhenDisa: Determines whether the plant is hidden while this device is disabled. SHOW LEAVES - Only the leaves will be visible while this device is disabled.
